source|FIX Session Layer Test Cases|1.0|https://dev.fixtrading.org/standards/fix-session-testcases-online/
case|1B.a|initiator|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1b-logon-initiator.nfscenario|FIX.4.4 initiator connect baseline|verify=verified|condition=Initiator establishes the transport connection to its peer|expected=Transport connection is established and the initiator can begin Logon processing|verified=transport-connected,outbound=1
case|1B.b|initiator|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1b-logon-initiator.nfscenario|FIX.4.4 initiator outbound Logon baseline|verify=verified|condition=Initiator sends its initial Logon request after connect|expected=Outbound Logon is sent with MsgSeqNum 1|verified=msg-type=A,msg-seq-num=1,outbound=1
case|1B.c|initiator|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1b-logon-initiator.nfscenario|FIX.4.4 initiator Logon acknowledgement baseline|verify=verified|condition=Initiator receives a valid Logon acknowledgement at the expected sequence number|expected=Session becomes active, emits no extra outbound FIX frame, and advances NextNumIn|verified=session-active,outbound=0,next-in-after=2
case|1B.d|initiator|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1bd-invalid-logon-ack-logout.nfscenario|initiator invalid Logon acknowledgement logs out and disconnects|verify=verified|condition=Initiator receives an invalid Logon acknowledgement|expected=Report an error, send Logout with diagnostic text, and disconnect|verified=error,logout,disconnect,session-disconnected
case|1B.e|initiator|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1be-first-response-not-logon.nfscenario|initiator non-Logon first response logs out and disconnects|verify=verified|condition=Initiator receives a first peer message other than Logon|expected=Report first-message-not-Logon error, send Logout, and disconnect|verified=error,logout,disconnect,session-disconnected
case|1S.a|acceptor|mandatory|FIX.4.2,FIX.4.4,FIXT.1.1|mapped|cases/1s-logon-acceptor-multiversion.nfscenario|acceptor Logon baseline across FIX.4.2 FIX.4.4 and FIXT.1.1|verify=verified|condition=Acceptor receives valid Logon requests for each supported transport version|expected=Respond with Logon acknowledgements and activate FIX.4.2, FIX.4.4, and FIXT.1.1 sessions|verified=fix42-active,fix44-active,fixt11-active,msg-type=A,msg-seq-num=1
case|1S.b|acceptor|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1sb-duplicate-identity.nfscenario|duplicate inbound identity disconnects without sending a FIX message|verify=verified|condition=Acceptor receives Logon with an identity already bound to an active connection|expected=Report an error and disconnect the duplicate attempt without sending a FIX message|verified=error,outbound=0,disconnect
case|1S.c|acceptor|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/1sc-unknown-identity.nfscenario|unknown inbound identity disconnects without sending a FIX message|verify=verified|condition=Acceptor receives Logon with an unauthenticated or unconfigured identity|expected=Report an error and disconnect without sending a FIX message|verified=error,outbound=0,disconnect
case|1S.d|acceptor|mandatory|FIXT.1.1|mapped|cases/1s-fixt11-missing-default-appl-ver.nfscenario|FIXT invalid Logon subset using missing DefaultApplVerID|verify=verified|condition=Acceptor receives an invalid FIXT.1.1 Logon missing DefaultApplVerID|expected=Report an error, send Logout with diagnostic text, and disconnect|verified=error,logout,disconnect,session-disconnected
case|2S|acceptor|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2s-first-message-not-logon.nfscenario|acceptor first message is not Logon|verify=verified|condition=Acceptor receives a first inbound message other than Logon|expected=Disconnect without sending a FIX message and report an error condition before processing session sequence state|verified=outbound=0,disconnect,error,next-in-after=1
case|2.a|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2a-valid-msgseqnum-accept.nfscenario|valid MsgSeqNum acceptance baseline|verify=verified|condition=Inbound MsgSeqNum equals expected NextNumIn|expected=Accept the message and advance NextNumIn without outbound reject or logout|verified=outbound=0,next-in-after=3,session-active
case|2.b|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2b-msgseq-high-resend.nfscenario|high inbound MsgSeqNum triggers ResendRequest|verify=verified|condition=Inbound MsgSeqNum is higher than expected|expected=Send ResendRequest for the missing sequence range without advancing NextNumIn|verified=inbound-seq=4,msg-type=2,begin-seq=2,end-seq=3,next-in-after=2
case|2.c|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2c-msgseq-low-logout.nfscenario|low inbound MsgSeqNum logout baseline|verify=verified|condition=Inbound MsgSeqNum is lower than expected and PossDupFlag is not Y|expected=Report an error, send Logout with stale sequence text, and disconnect|verified=error,logout,disconnect,session-disconnected
case|2.d|all|mandatory|FIX.4.2,FIX.4.4,FIXT.1.1|mapped|cases/2d-garbled-message-warning.nfscenario|garbled raw frame ignored without advancing inbound sequence|verify=verified|condition=Inbound message is garbled|expected=Generate warning, ignore the message, and keep NextNumIn unchanged|verified=warning,outbound=0,next-in-unchanged,subsequent-valid-message-accepted
case|2.e|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2e-possdup-duplicate-accept.nfscenario|PossDup duplicate heartbeat acceptance baseline|verify=verified|condition=PossDupFlag is Y, OrigSendingTime is not later than SendingTime, and MsgSeqNum is lower than expected for an already seen message|expected=Ignore or accept the duplicate without outbound reject and keep the session active|verified=inbound-possdup=1,outbound=0,next-in-after=3,session-active
case|2.f|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2f-possdup-origsendingtime-late-reject.nfscenario|late OrigSendingTime on PossDup rejected with accuracy problem|verify=verified|condition=PossDupFlag is Y and OrigSendingTime is later than SendingTime|expected=Reject with SessionRejectReason 10, report an error, and advance NextNumIn|verified=inbound-possdup=1,reject,reject-reason=10,ref-msg-type=0,error,next-in-after=3
case|2.g|all|mandatory|FIX.4.4|mapped|cases/2g-possdup-missing-origsendingtime.nfscenario|PossDup without OrigSendingTime reject baseline|verify=verified|condition=PossDupFlag is Y without OrigSendingTime|expected=Reject with RefTagID 122 and SessionRejectReason 1 while advancing NextNumIn|verified=ref-tag=122,reject-reason=1,next-in-after=3
